This is a personal fork of [[efurlanm/mermaid-tw5|https://github.com/efurlanm/mermaid-tw5]], which itself consolidated several earlier community forks. I am not the original author — all credit goes to the contributors listed below. This copy has been updated and improved for personal use.

!! What changed in this fork

;2026-04-27 (0.5.0)
:Upgrade Mermaid to [[11.14.0|https://github.com/mermaid-js/mermaid/releases/tag/v11.14.0]] — adds mindmap, timeline, Sankey, XY chart, quadrant, block, architecture, kanban, packet diagrams and more (20 types total)
:Async render support for Mermaid 10+/11 API (Promise-based `render()`)
:Friendly error display — shows diagram source and error message instead of a raw exception
:Lazy loading — mermaid.js and D3.js are deferred until the first diagram is rendered; pages without diagrams pay no loading cost
:Test suite — 13 automated tests covering widget rendering and parser behaviour
:GitHub Actions CI/CD — automated tests on push and GitHub Pages deployment
:Contributor docs — README and CONTRIBUTING.md for developer setup
;2024-03-18 (0.3.8)
:Add "About $$$ usage", by [[linonetwo|https://github.com/efurlanm/mermaid-tw5/pull/8]] (thanks)
:Add pan and zoom via D3.js click interaction, by [[fkmiec|https://github.com/efurlanm/mermaid-tw5/pull/5]] (thanks)
:Update TiddlyWiki to 5.3.3
