!! Bundle size

The plugin adds ~3.4&nbsp;MB to the empty TiddlyWiki 5.3.3 file (2.4&nbsp;MB): 3.1&nbsp;MB for Mermaid 11.14.0 and 0.26&nbsp;MB for D3.js v6. Both libraries are lazy-loaded — a tiddler with no diagrams pays no cost on render.

!! How to use

''Widget syntax'' — inline anywhere in a tiddler:

```
<$mermaid text="
flowchart LR
    A --> B --> C
"/>
```

<$mermaid text="
flowchart LR
    A --> B --> C
"/>

''Block syntax'' — using `$$$` delimiters:

```
$$$text/vnd.tiddlywiki.mermaid
flowchart TD
    A --> B
$$$
```

$$$text/vnd.tiddlywiki.mermaid
flowchart TD
    A --> B
$$$

''Tiddler type'' — set a tiddler's type to `text/vnd.tiddlywiki.mermaid` and write the diagram directly as the tiddler body (no widget or delimiters needed). It can then be transcluded with `{{TiddlerName}}` elsewhere.

''Pan and zoom'' — click any rendered diagram to toggle pan & zoom mode. Click again to exit.

See the [[Mermaid Chart Catalog]] for syntax and examples of all 20 supported diagram types.

